# Development Philosophy

## Testing

- Use Vitest for tests
- One-to-one test file mapping (source → .test.ts)
- Mock external dependencies; test real implementation
- Use `vi.useFakeTimers()` for time-dependent code

## Code Quality

- Never disable ESLint rules to hide problems; fix root cause
- Refactor complex functions; never increase complexity thresholds
- Preserve documentation when refactoring

## File Length

- Max 250 lines per file
- Extract modules when exceeding limit; never compress code
